title: My First Tumblr Art Raffle!
body:
So I realized I hit 150 watchers…Yay!!!

For promoting my art and making more new friends, I want to start an art raffle!

It’s easy to join, you have to be a follower, and then reblog this so more people can see! But please don’t just watch me for free art and then unwatch…

I will pick 3 winners! 

the first winner get 2 full body characters w/o background or 1 full body w/ background! Here are some examples:

The second winner get a half body drawing! Will be something like this:

And then the third winner will get a headshot like this:

The deadline is December 25! I’ll pick winner by using number picking sites. Good Luck guys!
